                    	<note xml:id="n_remarks" type="remarks">
                    	    
                                    
<p>The 10-centimes postcard has on the side with the message the postmark: ‘ST REMY DE PROVCE 17 / JUIL / 89’, and on the side bearing the address (twice): ‘ARLES BOUCHES DU RHONE 5e|16 / JUIL / <hi rend="italics">[</hi>89<hi rend="italics">]</hi>’. The address reads: ‘<hi rend="italics">[</hi>M<hi rend="italics">]</hi>r Vincent, chez Mr le docteur/ Peyron, à/ St Remy/ B du R’.</p>
    <p>Jansen 1998.</p>
                                    
                                
                    	</note>
                    
                </listAnnotation>
